{"tid":2222704,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"༄༊࿆CNNIC公佈中國互聯網報告，數據指中國有9.4億網民，2成人收入不足$1000༊࿆࿐","createTime":"2020-09-29T09:09:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T10:18:39.000Z","uid":38539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"087a3f14a499c5a182dec47de0ac9f626afc28d8","tid":2222704,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:09:25.000Z","msg":"據＃第46次中國互聯網絡發展狀況統計報告＃顯示，截至2020年6月，中國網民規模為9.40億，互聯網普及率達67.0％。其中，農村網民規模為28.5億，佔網民整體的30.4％ 。平均每月收入在2001-5000元的網民群體佔比為32.6％；月收入在5000元以上的網民群體佔比為24.2％；有收入但月收入在1000元及以下的網民群體佔比 為21.0％。<br />\n<br />\n月收入已包括<br />\n學生收入包括家庭提供的生活費，勤工儉學工資，獎學金及其他收入；<br />\n農林牧漁勞動人員收入包括子女提供的生活費，農業生產收入，政府補貼等收入；<br />\n無業/下崗/失業人員收入包括子女給 的生活費，政府救濟，補貼，撫卹金，低保等；<br />\n退休人員收入包括子女提供的生活費，退休金等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zs5c7Ze.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzs5c7Ze.jpg&h=da3c8017&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LHJBQcA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLHJBQcA.png&h=269ef507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uWBDi5V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuWBDi5V.png&h=52c243a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a0808c9d01950683f0cab57842fa52298085f49","tid":2222704,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:11:46.000Z","msg":"大陸上網好平，月入一千都交得起上網費 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee05a42f36ca578187f3653deddaf6e1f18a3164","tid":2222704,"uid":118647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6a0808c9d01950683f0cab57842fa52298085f49","tid":2222704,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:11:46.000Z","msg":"大陸上網好平，月入一千都交得起上網費 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T09:14:52.000Z","msg":"唔洗$40一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid